\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Status of the twelve refactor-brief items. $\dagger $ Earth occlusion, phase-angle filter and heavy-tailed noise are in; motion blur is deferred. $\ddagger $ Three scenarios cover the requested geometries (halo at L1 in CR3BP and SPICE, plus an NRHO at L2-S); a ``bad-observability'' geometry case is straightforward to add as a fourth registered scenario.}}{3}{table.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
